            <p>
                We won't be liable to you for any damages that arise from your using the Services.
                This includes if the Services are hacked or unavailable.
                This includes all types of damages (indirect, incidental, consequential,
                special or exemplary). And it includes all kinds of legal claims,
                such as breach of contract, breach of warranty, tort, or any other loss.
            </p>

            <h2>Severability</h2>

