                If any provision of these terms is found invalid by a court of competent
                jurisdiction, you agree that the court should try to give effect to the parties'
                intentions as reflected in the provision and that other provisions
                of the Terms will remain in full effect.
            </p>

            <hr>

            <p>This page was last updated on August 25th, 2025.</p>
        </main>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .container {
        display: flex;
        width: 100%;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    main {
        max-width: 80ch;
        width: 80ch;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    p {
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    ul {
        font-size: 24px;
    }

    .footnote {
        font-size: 24px;
    }
</style>